{
  "stem": "23742.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I was 18, I had the all-important task of being appointed assistant factory manager in the clothing industry, which is where I met my future wife.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I worked in that company for-- until I was 21.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a great deal of unrest in Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very evident that war was coming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not exactly when, but it was coming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the government decreed that all men of the age of 21 would join the army for six-months training, obviously, in preparation of war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And as I was 21 at the time, on the 1st of July, 1939, which prior to the outbreak of war, I, I was conscripted into the army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I joined the Royal Corps of Signals in Catterick in Yorkshire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I trained as a dispatch rider.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Our training continued.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then September the third of that year, war was declared.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On November the 5th, I was with a unit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we embarked for France as the initial unit of the British Expeditionary Force.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we landed in Cherbourg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We traveled across France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we established our headquarters in Arras, which is a  town in Northern France.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my, my unit was not a combat one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We were communications.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We provided the support and communications from headquarters to the forward troops.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the winter of '39 was comparatively quiet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The German army was busy elsewhere, mainly in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a very bad winter, '39, '40.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then of course, in the spring of 1940, the German army broke through the Maginot Line, which is in Southern France.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And their rapid-- advance was quite rapid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They, they were a superior force.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they swept across Southern France, up towards Paris and towards the, and towards the coast.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
